# Styling guidance for Tailwind CSS

- Always provide a light and dark variation for all colors using Tailwind CSS
    - eg. "text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300 hover:bg-zinc-300 dark:hover:bg-zinc-700 bg-zinc-300 dark:bg-zinc-700 border border-zinc-300 dark:border-zinc-700"
    - While you will not always use hover and border, the key is to properly set both regular and dark values whenever you do use color.
